trans-unit.source: Provides a listener that routes all tracing and debugging output to the IIS 7.0 infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Fornece um ouvinte que roteia todas as saídas de rastreamento e depuração para a infraestrutura de IIS 7.0.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.IisTraceListener> class connects the tracing mechanism of [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] to [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.IisTraceListener> classe conecta o mecanismo de rastreamento de [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] para [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: This listener class enables developers who create [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] applications and who implement the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> and <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interfaces to raise page-level, module-level, or handler-level events to the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] infrastructure when tracing is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe de ouvinte permite que os desenvolvedores que criam [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] aplicativos e que implementem o <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> e <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interfaces para gerar eventos de nível de página, nível de módulo ou manipulador de nível para o [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] infraestrutura quando o rastreamento está habilitada.

trans-unit.source: This listener class does not route [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] events to ASP.NET classes.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe de ouvinte não encaminhar [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] eventos para classes do ASP.NET.

trans-unit.source: This includes the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> class and classes that implement the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> or <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interface.
trans-unit.target: Isso inclui o <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> classe e classes que implementam o <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> ou <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interface.
